# Copy to .env.local (dev) or set in launchd plist / shell profile (prod).
# None of these are required — they override defaults.

# Obsidian vault scanned by chat retrieval, quick capture, Notion sync, and classifier.
# Default: ~/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/icloud-shared/Obsidian/Obsidian Vault
# VAULT_PATH=/Users/you/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/icloud-shared/Obsidian/Obsidian Vault

# Directory scanned by `npm run sync:projects` for git repos.
# Default: ~/Work
# WORK_DIR=/Users/you/Work

# Directory read by `npm run sync:agents` for JSON agent configs.
# Default: ~/.dashboard/agents
# AGENT_CONFIG_DIR=/Users/you/.dashboard/agents

# Hostname to bind when running `npm start` in production.
# Set to 0.0.0.0 to accept connections from other Tailscale peers.
# HOSTNAME=0.0.0.0

# Port for Next.js.
# PORT=3000
